      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Folkert van Heusden</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:172px;\"><a href=\"https://www.csvn.nl/index.php/nieuws/51-toernooien/640-pt46-round-2\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/7/71/FolkertvanHeusden.jpg\" width=\"170\" height=\"196\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:FolkertvanHeusden.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Folkert van Heusden <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Folkert van Heusden</b>,<br />\na Dutch software developer <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nAs <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en2.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_source_movement\">open source</a> and game programmer, Folkert is author of the experimental chess programs <a href=\"/index.php?title=Pos&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Pos (page does not exist)\">Pos</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/DeepBrutePos\" title=\"DeepBrutePos\">DeepBrutePos</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, both written in <a href=\"/Java\" title=\"Java\">Java</a>. A incarnation of DeepBrutePos, running on a system with an <a href=\"/UDOO\" title=\"UDOO\">UDOO</a> computer and seven <a href=\"/Raspberry_Pi\" title=\"Raspberry Pi\">Raspberry Pi</a> calculating nodes is dubbed <a href=\"/PuppetMaster\" title=\"PuppetMaster\">PuppetMaster</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> . Former chess programs were <a href=\"/Embla\" title=\"Embla\">Embla</a> (in 2016 incorporated inside a self made <a href=\"/index.php?title=Embla_Board&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Embla Board (page does not exist)\">chess computer board</a> based on a <a href=\"/Raspberry_Pi#3\" title=\"Raspberry Pi\">Raspberry Pi 3</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>), <a href=\"/index.php?title=CPP1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"CPP1 (page does not exist)\">CPP1</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> , <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bullucks&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bullucks (page does not exist)\">Bullucks</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> and <a href=\"/index.php?title=QueenBee&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"QueenBee (page does not exist)\">QueenBee</a>. His latest chess engine, first released in June 2019, is the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant <a href=\"/Micah\" title=\"Micah\">Micah</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>.  He started writing chess programs on May 21, 1996 (aprox 14:30).\nHe further wrote the <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a> playing program <i>Stop</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>.\nOther new chess programs: <a href=\"/Feeks\" title=\"Feeks\">Feeks</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=CaffeinatedPawn&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"CaffeinatedPawn (page does not exist)\">CaffeinatedPawn</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Dolly&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Dolly (page does not exist)\">Dolly</a> and <a href=\"/Dog\" title=\"Dog\">Dog</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2012_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2012 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folkert_van_Heusden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2012_...\">2012 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folkert_van_Heusden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2012 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=52125&amp;sid=d3919159e42267a64891e4e0e3bfbaf0\">move generation speed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, January 03, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=472906\">what on earth</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48735\">transposition tables</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 23, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49892\">raspberry pi cluster versus fairymax</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 31, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Raspberry_Pi\" title=\"Raspberry Pi\">Raspberry Pi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52280&amp;start=11\">Re: CSVN 1st Open Internet Tournament: Results and games</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 12, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53820\">std::vector&lt;&gt; considered harmful</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 25, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_List\" title=\"Move List\">Move List</a>, <a href=\"/Array\" title=\"Array\">Array</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folkert_van_Heusden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56770\">creating an opening book</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 24, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57391\">Embla</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 26, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58525\">Embla 0.7.1</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 08, 2015</li></ul>\n<p><b>2016</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58996\">late move reduction</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 21, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58900\">Embla 0.8</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2016 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59419\">Embla 0.9</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59423\">threading</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59977\">chess computer board</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 27, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Embla_Board&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Embla Board (page does not exist)\">Embla Board</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59984\">cluster versus single server</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 28, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2017</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=62737\">improving iid</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 06, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Internal_Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Internal Iterative Deepening\">Internal Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65477\">cut nodes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 18, 2017 &#160;» <a href=\"/Node_Types#CUT\" title=\"Node Types\">Cut-Nodes</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65490\">PVS &amp; Embla</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 19, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation_Search\" title=\"Principal Variation Search\">Principal Variation Search</a>, <a href=\"/Embla\" title=\"Embla\">Embla</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65799\">tuning for the uninformed</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 23, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2018</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67614\">texel tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68278&amp;start=16\">Re: Lazy SMP ideas</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a>, <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=68692\">easy move?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 19, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Time_Management\" title=\"Time Management\">Time Management</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71062\">open files and diagonals</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Folkert van Heusden</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 21, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Open_File\" title=\"Open File\">Open File</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folkert_van_Heusden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/folkertvanheusden\">folkertvanheusden (Folkert van Heusden) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vanheusden.com/\">www.vanheusden.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.vanheusden.com/chess/\">Computer Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-go.info/db/operson.php?a=van+Heusden%2C+Folkert\">van Heusden, Folkert</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computer-go.info/\">computer-go.info</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Folkert_van_Heusden&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Folkert van Heusden operating <a href=\"/PuppetMaster\" title=\"PuppetMaster\">PuppetMaster</a> at <a href=\"/PT_46\" title=\"PT 46\">PT 46</a>, photos by <a href=\"/Jan_Krabbenbos\" title=\"Jan Krabbenbos\">Jan Krabbenbos</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.csvn.nl/index.php/nieuws/51-toernooien/640-pt46-round-2\">PT46: Round 2</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nl.linkedin.com/in/folkertvanheusden\">Folkert van Heusden - LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.vanheusden.com/pos/\">POS - An experimental chess program</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span cl